      "date": "2020-01-15 22:50:18.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review+1\n\n(1 comment)\n\nIn short:\n- the req_capsule_field_present() can be used alone on client when checking reply fields.\n- req_capsule_has_field() is needed when requests with different formats are being processed by server along with req_capsule_field_present() for compatibility checks.\n- req_capsule_has_field can be used while preparing reply if different formats are being prepared by some common code.",
